<div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-0 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">

  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-xl">
    Contact DVLA
  </h1>
</div>
    </div>
    <div class="article-container group govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <div class="content-block">
        <div class="inner">
          
  <div class="intro">
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
      <p>Use this service to find the right phone number, email or postal address for <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr>. They can help with things like:</p>

<ul>
  <li>vehicle tax or a Statutory Off Road Notification (<abbr title="Statutory Off Road Notification">SORN</abbr>)</li>
  <li>driving licences and applications</li>
  <li>number plates and log books (V5C documents)</li>
  <li>health conditions and driving</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="find-contact-details-for-dvla">Find contact details for <abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr>
</h2>



